Hexaware's Agentic AI claims solution transforms the overall claims lifecycle by enabling intelligent FNOL, AI-assisted adjuster workflows, proactive SIU investigation, and faster, more customer-centric claim resolution experiences. The solution experience is demonstrated across three key personas: 

the policyholder, the adjuster, and the SIU investigator. 

The policyholder experiences a simplified and intelligent FNOL journey, enabling faster claim reporting, AI-assisted intake validation, real-time claim tracking, and seamless communication throughout the claims lifecycle. The adjuster is empowered with AI-assisted claim assessment, document intelligence, fraud insights, 

Repair vs. replacement recommendations, and intelligent decision support to accelerate claim handling while maintaining human oversight. 

The SIU Investigator gains proactive fraud investigation capabilities through AI-driven fraud indicators, investigation timelines, external verification support, SLA tracking, and centralized access to all claim-related intelligence required for deeper investigation and compliance review. So let's start with the policyholder interactive claim journey. 

